      exact ⟨ ∑ i ∈ Finset.range n, ‖p.coeff i‖, fun i hi => Finset.single_le_sum ( fun i _ => norm_nonneg ( p.coeff i ) ) hi ⟩;
    -- Using the bounds on the coefficients, we can bound the right-hand side of the inequality.
